Emhart Corp said it receivedfour contracts valued at a total of seven mln dlrs to design,develop and install data communications and automateddispatching systems.    The company said its Planning Research Corp unit, whichreceived the contracts, will do the work for the city of GrandRapids, Mich., the New Jersey Transit Authority, the LosAngeles County Sheriff's office and the city of Calgary,Alberta, Canada. Reuter&#3;